<TEXT>I am totally pleased with this car! The looks are fresh and cool and the preformance is way beyond my old Grand Am. The car feels solid and is realatively quiet on the road. Also the controls and buttons are well laid out and easy to operate on the go. For the price, the amount of features and innovations is impossible to beat. Also, given the size of the car, it is incredibly roomy in front and back. The driving position is higher, and the dash is lower and pushed back giving great visability. What a great step up in all aspects. The warranty is nice too. Ask about Pontiac's new policy with 5yr bumper to bumper. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>The sunroof is sweet! Also, the red illumination at night gives the car a sportier feel. I also really like the driver information center and the awesome sound system!</FAVORITE>
